<br>
Vermillion Robe of Torrefaction:<br>
625 damage / 15 sec / 0 mana = 41.667 dps<br>
<br>
Meditation Rate:<br>
@65 = ~30 mana per tick = 5 mana per second<br>
<br>
Strike of Solusek:<br>
2740 damage / 640 mana = 4.28 dpm<br>
(focus / scm: 20% damage / 40% mana reduction)<br>
3288 damage /  mana = ~8.56 dpm<br>
<br>
If your meditation rate if 5 mana per second, then 5 mana * 4.28 dpm = sustained rate of 21.4 dps<br>
<br>
or<br>
<br>
5 mana * 8.56 dpm = 42.8 dps<br>
<br>
So...what am I saying here?<br>
<br>
